_sText:
Welcome to the real Mushroom Kingdom. Where Mario is a mushroom addicted mafia man and Bowser is a kidnapping pedofile. In this map travel to Mario's house (Set ablaze by some angry shyguys before Mario taught them a lesson) and the Mushroom Kingdom jail where Bowser recently had a failed escape attempt and Yoshi's interogation for a halloween egg throwing has gone terribly wrong. Have fun looking through the chaos and adding more to it in this Mario map!
